im doing good.
i cant stop smiling.
i love it.
and im happy.



<3

wellllll summer is going good so far...i went to my lil brudders bball game last night with spencer....i was bummed that there were no fights...haha that would have been fun to see...but everyone played good, and of course they won... ummmmm i had work today than, me and pat went to CPK, the thai pizze is muy good. yea..i am boooored... ok bye

so i did kickboxing on thursday morning and i am way sore haha, i prolly havnt had a decent work out in a year! well today was fun....haha i went to work at 730 then i got home at 12 ate, talked on the phone for like 1/2 hour.....then i slept from like 130 to 5 then spencer called me and woke me up, so we talked on the phone for like an hour....wow thats a nice waste of a day....and i cant go anywhere tonight bc i DONT HAVE A CAR YET! and no one else is home to take me....hmmm what to do what to do....so i am gonna hit up hurricane harbour sometime soon ya, i havnt been there in a while....whelps that is about it...haha

so im prety stoked sumemr is here, and its already been way good. last night was probably one of the funnest nights ever, and itll prolly be one of my fav memories from this sumemr. ok well i dont know what else to say, oh i hate it when people are dumb, assume things(even when they assume right they still have to business getting into other ppls business) and then they get mad at you, give you dirty looks, and ignore you  just bc they assumed something.WOW!


<3

I GOT MY LISCENCE!!!!!!!!

holy crap i cant believe i actually passed!! ahh this is soo good!!

who is getting their liscence tomorrow?
sherry is getting her liscence tomorrow
and she is SOOO excited




oh, story, so i was driving around my neighborhood, for one last drive before the big test tomorrow morning, and so all of a sudden i see this guy and this girl walking around my neighborhood, and i took a closer look, and it was taylor butler and elya fletcher. which i thought was way weird considering niether of them live near me.... yaa not that exciting, but i didnt know what else to write haha....well wish me luck for my driving test tomorrow at 1030!!!

o.m.g i relaly think i am gonna die. i went to the beach yesterday with shannon colin robin and spencer, and i got extreeeeeeemly burnt. like the back of my legs look like death, and it feels worse than it looks. it hurts soooooooooo bad to sit down, so school today was like really ow. it was very painful. ahhhhhh haha when i woke up this morning i started crying because it hurt sooo bad. and my shoulders still hurt from sunday when i got burned. they are all blistery and my science teacher said it looked like a 3rd degree burn and i was like noooooooo i dont want to get skin cancer....ahhhhhhh it hurts soooo bad to move at all. i cant even walk normal w/o it hurting like hades! ahh ok enough of my complaing haha....later!!

so pretty much i am gonna die, because i am waaay sunburned. i was at the park, then i wen to annas house, andwent swimming allll dya with a bunch of ppl, and yea it was way fun, we had chicen fights n stuff, and me n owen totally won! but work is going pretty good. i got my first paycheck on friday, it was  $100 and that was for only working a week. so i am pretty happy. and this week we are getting a $55 bonus bc we got tons of new patients! haha yesss!! wow i am reeeally tired right now. oh i am going to the beach tomoro!! yess i am so excited!! yaya!! its gonna be soooo fun.

oh on friday, i walked aound the mall pregnant. it was quite funny. i got so many weird looks!! haha oh btw it was fo the jr. highers for my church. i didnt just randomly decide to walk around the mall pregnant. but everyone saidn i am gonna be a cute pregnant lady! haha

ok so rachels 16th bithday party was last night, and omg it was sooo fun!! it was at a restraunt in westlake, and we had dinner and dancing on the patio. it was like the party of the century!! lol umm me n shanon and gannon got randy to dance for us, but in the parking lot, he didnt want to do it in front of evryone, so he did it for the 3 of us, hes so modest haha but hes so good, and you srsly wouldnt expect like randy to be a like a way good hip-hop dancer!! but then we went back in and rachel found out that he danced for us, so he was like ok one more time for rachel, so the 5 of us went back out there, then we came back and anna found out, and she was like what!?!? i wanna see, so randy was all ok this is the last time for reals. so he did it!! hes awesome. me n shan are going to his dance recital in june. um so anyways.. good job to evryone who competed yesterday and sorry to all the freshman who my brother made you do really dumb/gross stuff while playing truth or dare on the bus ride home. you guys are brave!! haha and congrats to lynne, matt, and margaret who made it to cif finals! you guys are awesome!!! so i am pretty exited because i have half days on mon tue and wed!! how awesome is that!! yay! i am so excited! oh btw i start working tomoro! i am nervous!! eek! but angela is training me, so its gonna be way fun, buuuuut we are gonna get like nothing done!! haha me and angela harris = not doing what we are supposed to be doing!! lol haha

ok so i just got my first job ever!! and i start on monday!! i start at $7 then after training i get a raise, and i get weekly bonuses! i am so excited!  yay! oh and its at agoura family chiropractic so if you ever need to get your back adjusted thats the place to go!! oh and another thing is the hours are way good, mon wed fri 3-6 and saturday 8-12 so i dont work any nights, and i practically have all day saturday free! and then of course during the summer i will get longer hours, but it will still be good becuase no nights! and its not everyday!

it is SO nice to be able to come home at 2 oclock! it is absolutly wonderful that track is over!












why cant i forget about you?
i tried, but i cant.

ok i am so happy! my wierd disease is going away!! yess i am so glad it didnt last 10 weeks like it couldve!! it only lasted like 5 weeks! ok well i hope everybody is having a wonderful mothers day! 





i saw marshall at church today...haha














...................................................................................................................................................................

so, i am pretty much not excited at all for finals tomorrow. last year i was sooooo excited, and this year i just cant wait for tomorrow to be over, cuz i hate track so much. well guess its not exactly track, its my team. but yaaaa last yea was so fun with the 4x4 it was the best ever, like we won league fianls and stuff, it was me, aimee gibbons, nicole kale, and sarah cox. and we owned that race, it was awesome! awwwww i miss it sooo much! =( and now this year the only team we havnt lost to is calabasas, wow! big yay for us. wow pity party for me haha i am in such a bad mood, since yesterday. it sucks. i like being happy. i saw heather russel the other day and it made me happy. i miss last year study hall with her and allison. haha it was fun. mr lyne hated us. haha ok well enough of me missing last year. bye! haha see you tomoro!!!!! and good luck!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
i just dyed my hair!! yay!

wow only i more week of track, i am SO excited!! i hate track so much....um im excited to see everyone tommorrow at prelims, and then agian on friday at finals. yesss um disneyland was way fun. but i decided i dont like going with parents and little kids as much as i like going with normal people.....but i stil loved going with my babies!! ummm yea i think thats it...

so, my whole entire family(immediate) is here, and my house is soo crowded!! like there is 13 poeple in my house, and my house is not that big, so yea, its crazy.

i went to cvd last night with shannon,angelica,cody,nick,gannon,landon,and spencer, then later we met up with max,michael cradeur haha,john,and jacob. it was way fun. and i totally beat up michael craduer. it was cool. and then gannon and cody adn spencer drew wiht sharpie all over my face!!! and lower back. and spencer wrote his name REALLY big on both my arms. and on shannons arm too. but they also drew a bunch of other crap on shannons arms. ummmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmm i saw alyse n sean, that was cool. then i saw lucas borough, and i talked to them all for a bit, and embarresed myself in front of this girl, for lucas, haha yaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa. ok well i gonna go to santa barbara soon!! i cant wait!! and i am sooo happy becasue me and pat didnt have to go to school again today, haha and for like no reason again! but my other sister adn bro-in-law got here last night. yay! party at my house lol. um ok i got to go get ready for SB. later!!
cvd tonight, i am pretty excited!! yes!!

so i am really bored, and itchy. i cant wait until my freaking disease goes away!! ahh i hate it. it sucks! and its suppossed to take 10 weeks to get better. and its only been 2 weeks. so its until SUMMER i have this freaking disease. ahhhhhhhhhhhhh i hate it. and it gets worse like every day. everyday i get more and more bumps, and i get more and more itchy ahhhhhhhhhhh. my coach got fired. what up with me and not being able to get away from coaches being fired?!?! oh well. at least there is only one 2 mroe weeks of track left. and 2 more track meets. i seriously cant wait till its over. i hate it so much. i turned in my application for cold stones today... yea i hope i get the job becasue i dont wanna apply somewhere else cuz i am to lazy! haha if i dont get the job i will prolly work at jamba juice. yaaaaaaaaaaa ok
oh man i am soo tired!! and its retarded, cuzits not like ive been super busy or anything. ahhhhhhhhhhh

hello frens, i have good news- i am not contagious!!
ok soo i went to the doctor, and the other retard doctor i went to on monday mis-diagnosed me, and i really dont have scabies, i have pityriasis rosea... and i am NOT contagious! but it sucks because there is no way to make them go away. until they go away naturally. and thats gonna take like a couple weeks at least. so that sucks. i am juts happy that i am not contagious! oh, and i am way stoked because my mom said i dont have to go to spartan relays tomoro!! yess!!! i am soo happy! ok well yea its been prety nicenot being at school, i went to taco bell with my bro, sis,bro-in-law,other sis, and my 3 nieces. it was way good. ok bye haha



-share ee-

so i didnt go to school today, becuase when i woke up i felt like i was hit by a car....i was soooooooo tired, and i am sunburned, buuuuut i have to go to the doctor again because of my scabies. they got worse, adn now i have soooo many more bumps. so i guess htey medicine thing i did on monday didnt work. haha sorry if i am contagious and got you scabies. oh btw they could take up to 6 weeks to show up. sorry!! but maybe i dont even have scabies and that is why the medicine didnt work. gosh i really hope it goes away soon whatever it is, cuz it itches like no other

ok so my babies got here from boston today, and they are soooo cute!! i hadnt seen them since last june, and they have changed soo much!! like one of them can read, another one can talk so good, and they all grew soo much! ahh they are SO cute!! ok well yea haha

omg i was sooooo hyper today, like anything made me laugh and i laughed so hard that 3 times i stated crying!! haha it was awesome!!  


and nobody believes me, but i really am not contagious anymore!!! haha

so i went to the doctor to see about my scabies, and the doctor was SO retarded. he was seriously dumb... ah! ok so i got some lotion stuff to put on before bed that will kill the scabie bugs, and yea. 



OH GUESS WHAT?!?! my babies are coming from boston tomorrow!! i am sooooooo excited! i havnt seen them in almost a year!
